Which of the following commands will change the default gateway to 192.168.1.1using eth0?
A)  ip route default gw 168.1.1
B)  ip route change default via 168.1.1 dev eth0
C)  ip route default gw update 168.1.1
D)  ip route update default 168.1.1 eth0
B
B. The ip route command can be used for this purpose, and its syntax uses a changecommand and the via keyword. The same operation could be completed with the routecommand but would require deleting the existing gateway first and then re- adding a newdefault gateway.
